{"tid":1467573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）搞機場搞到分化晒，不如搞貨櫃碼頭？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:22:54.000Z","uid":154709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5e0e25cae4ff8b4951868c246a394dec8b9c82","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"大陸好多貨都經香港出口，一隻櫃30噸，裏面全部擺糖擺朱古力都值成千萬，扣起佢地啲貨一定蝕到入肉，特別係啲會過期既野<br />\n<br />\n而家又話搞到外國人又大愛撚，唔係大是大非既野好易比人分化，不如對住啲死物唔洗錫住？<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係運輸撚對貨運唔熟，有冇人有好計"},{"pid":"2200175ec9ec143ac3b5a9215029b45cc364201d","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d77d13c4dbcce9ad40fcaaa7152ef9d54887213b","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"05daaf27f8d50a4e592fb9fe551d1e5449b3f5c0","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"008e6cc661fb040444d17eb8bbe290e9b8d6d4b2","tid":1467573,"uid":55351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n貨櫃佬多老粗, 一定好多口角<br />\n之後有暴力鏡頭<br />\n以往都好多同貨車司機嘈既問題 同強行係遊行路線行過"},{"pid":"5ca2b75a742dc9ee789fc7e4366990edb209f4f9","tid":1467573,"uid":19564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:49.000Z","msg":"貨櫃碼頭可以暴力清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a12ae35f07ff3fde01dec918c84275d397cd09","tid":1467573,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須保護100%和理非行動 <br />\n<br />\n我地可以提早決定100%和理非定 有後續 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察風向 破壞連登 咩淪陷 唔好信<br />\n<br />\n信左就中警察計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議民陣遊行必須 100%和理非 否則就當卧底</span>"},{"pid":"3eea0170ad9e245abb315e5ac622a6c07da9829a","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e295fe94a1fd63b92a6999bdba95285aa48a3a5c","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb4fb245c5064324441ceb52dbeee7db093abe63","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216a3ab84f0a871da6a5472ecb69639b273f82ce","tid":1467573,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"班職業司機同你死過......"},{"pid":"74f28c030b8e085eede9308d7b5239a9824defac","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216a3ab84f0a871da6a5472ecb69639b273f82ce","tid":1467573,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"班職業司機同你死過......"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"好多都係公司請𢭃人工姐<br />\n<br />\n一場運動總有野要犧牲"},{"pid":"72916a2c89c5bb23c7775e9d12a86eb034518395","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36f0084d49b374a64ad62ce43bc9d1ece9a14a95","tid":1467573,"uid":154709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008e6cc661fb040444d17eb8bbe290e9b8d6d4b2","tid":1467573,"uid":55351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n貨櫃佬多老粗, 一定好多口角<br />\n之後有暴力鏡頭<br />\n以往都好多同貨車司機嘈既問題 同強行係遊行路線行過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"有冇方法癱瘓成個貨運？<br />\n我覺得有智取既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\